raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Omg!
Mabel: Wasn't that exciting?
Mabel: img: mabel/84
Mabel: It's like we have our own friend group now!
Mabel: With Naomi, Caleb and even my professor too! 🥰 
Mabel: And of course you!! 😍
- Naomi seems cool
	Player: Naomi seems cool
	Player: And busy
	Mabel: She's always like super busy 😵🥹
	Mabel: But she texts me when she has time 🥰
	Mabel: I feel like I'm seriously lucky to have a friend like her already
- Ooh Caleb huh? 😏 [if Story.has_flag(\"LUST\") && Story.has_flag(\"NaomiAssist\")]
	Player: Ooh Caleb huh? 😏
	Mabel: What do you mean? 😶
	Player: You know what I mean 😉
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: BABE OMG
	Mabel: If you were here I'd hit you with a pillow 😭
	Player: Relax I was only teasing 😁
	Mabel: Seriously 😩
	do heart(0)
	Mabel: You're such a meanie
- I could see why you really like your professor 👀
	Player: I could see why you really like your professor 👀
	Mabel: Really?
	Mabel: I feel like I got so lucky 
Mabel: Even Alice joined
Mabel: Naomi convinced her yay 🤭
Mabel: Though she seemed like she didn't say much
Mabel: Is it cause she's just shy? 🤔
Player: Seems like she has a situation to feel that way
Mabel: I hope she's okay 😓
- Maybe she just needs a friend
	Player: Maybe she just needs a friend
	Mabel: Maybe!
	Mabel: I'll see what I can do!
	Mabel: img: mabel/85
- I think she'll come around
	Player: I think she'll come around
	Mabel: I hope so!
	Mabel: Maybe it'll be a good community for her to cheer up
Mabel: I don't know that other girl though
Mabel: Paige I think?
Mabel: She was so chatty 😆
- She was a bit chatty
	Player: She was a bit chatty
	Mabel: Right!??
	Mabel: But maybe she's nice 😅
- Kinda like you sometimes!
	Player: Kinda like you sometimes!
	Mabel: Omg no way 🥺
	Mabel: Seriously?? I gotta watch myself from now on omg
	Mabel: img: mabel/86
- She seemed nice
	Player: She seemed nice
	Mabel: Maybe 😅
	Mabel: I got a bit overwhelmed though 😵
Mabel: I hope I can use this club as an excuse to spend more time with you hehehe
- I'll try my best
	Player: I'll try my best
	Mabel: 🥰
- So this was all a part of your plan huh?
	Player: So this was all a part of your plan huh?
	Mabel: Maybe 🕵️‍♀️
	Mabel: A spy never reveals her mission briefings to the target
	Player: Oh man 😆
Mabel: Oki dokes
Mabel: Gonna do some homework now
if Story.has_flag(\"Date3\"):
	Mabel: But I'm gonna see you tomorrow for our date 😊
	Player: Yep!
	Mabel: Excitinggg
	Mabel: Can't wait hehe
Mabel: Talk later babe! ☺️
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
